{"tid":1558820,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"831警察插贓嫁禍果件事 冇記者問？大家忘記左？","createTime":"2019-09-10T14:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T11:42:16.000Z","uid":222970,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"23b750e54570a47d0855cbb99be922660d5f9019","tid":1558820,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">證據確鑿都冇人記者問？<br />\n大家唔該推返上熱門<br />\n推到聽日4點記者問為止<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(有片為證) 我發現到831警察插贓嫁禍 想偽造不利證據誤導法官<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545069\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545069</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好神奇咁跌左個gas mask出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDKNKje.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDKNKje.gif&h=8bd3dfd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察疑似刻意將一個明顯唔屬於佢既gas mask<br />\n放落佢身邊 疑似想偽造證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2kxaZv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2kxaZv.gif&h=fe0f5d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個唔屬於佢既gas mask就變左佢既不利證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cArDQZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcArDQZT.jpg&h=0b3ff8a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f9e06e46592bc6c13f73a8061b4e81fbf84ebf9","tid":1558820,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"原來上星期五好似有記者問過<br />\n但班狗好似話未有資料就算<br />\n<br />\n到左琴日今日已經再冇記者問<br />\n明明有片證據確鑿都可以當冇事？"},{"pid":"9f6310a80e384547f42d253001c38b091cfa44c7","tid":1558820,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a2753fe42e7d89ab0c9d1bcc6df68276cf5500","tid":1558820,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sm